19#include <sys/types.h>
20
21#include <stdlib.h>
22#include <unistd.h>
23
24#include "tmux.h"
25
26/*
27 * Respawn a window (restart the command). Kill existing if -k given.
28 */
29
30static enum cmd_retval cmd_respawn_window_exec(struct cmd *,
31 struct cmdq_item *);
32
33const struct cmd_entry cmd_respawn_window_entry = {
34 .name = "respawn-window",
35 .alias = "respawnw",
36
37 .args = { "c:kt:", 0, -1 },
38 .usage = "[-c start-directory] [-k] " CMD_TARGET_WINDOW_USAGE
39 " [command]",
40
41 .target = { 't', CMD_FIND_WINDOW, 0 },
42
43 .flags = 0,
44 .exec = cmd_respawn_window_exec
45};
46
47static enum cmd_retval
48cmd_respawn_window_exec(struct cmd *self, struct cmdq_item *item)
49{
50 struct args *args = self->args;
51 struct session *s = item->target.s;
52 struct winlink *wl = item->target.wl;
53 struct window *w = wl->window;
54 struct window_pane *wp;
55 struct client *c = cmd_find_client(item, NULL, 1);
56 struct environ *env;
57 const char *path = NULL, *cp;
58 char *cause, *cwd = NULL;
59 struct environ_entry *envent;
60
61 if (!args_has(self->args, 'k')) {
62 TAILQ_FOREACH(wp, &w->panes, entry) {
63 if (wp->fd == -1)
64 continue;
65 cmdq_error(item, "window still active: %s:%d", s->name,
66 wl->idx);
67 return (CMD_RETURN_ERROR);
68 }
69 }
70
71 wp = TAILQ_FIRST(&w->panes);
72 TAILQ_REMOVE(&w->panes, wp, entry);
73 layout_free(w);
74 window_destroy_panes(w);
75 TAILQ_INSERT_HEAD(&w->panes, wp, entry);
76 window_pane_resize(wp, w->sx, w->sy);
77
78 if (item->client != NULL && item->client->session == NULL)
79 envent = environ_find(item->client->environ, "PATH");
80 else
81 envent = environ_find(s->environ, "PATH");
82 if (envent != NULL)
83 path = envent->value;
84
85 if ((cp = args_get(args, 'c')) != NULL)
86 cwd = format_single(item, cp, c, s, NULL, NULL);
87
88 env = environ_for_session(s, 0);
89 if (window_pane_spawn(wp, args->argc, args->argv, path, NULL, cwd, env,
90 s->tio, &cause) != 0) {
91 cmdq_error(item, "respawn window failed: %s", cause);
92 free(cause);
93 environ_free(env);
94 free(cwd);
95 server_destroy_pane(wp, 0);
96 return (CMD_RETURN_ERROR);
97 }
98 environ_free(env);
99 free(cwd);
100
101 layout_init(w, wp);
102 window_pane_reset_mode(wp);
103 screen_reinit(&wp->base);
104 input_init(wp);
105 window_set_active_pane(w, wp);
106
107 recalculate_sizes();
108 server_redraw_window(w);
109
110 return (CMD_RETURN_NORMAL);
111}
